  <thing id="cThsCripSt" name="Crippling Strike" description="At 5th level, a Thayan slaver can sneak attack opponents with such precision that his blows weaken and hamper them. When the slaver damages an opponent with a sneak attack, that opponent also takes 1 point of temporary Strength damage. Ability points lost in this way return on their own at the rate of 1 point per day for each damaged ability." compset="ClSpecial" summary="Sneak attacks deal 1 point of Strength damage in addition to normal damage.">
