  <thing id="ioHthMFlam" name="Hathran Mask of Flame" description="This mask is red with flames drawn in black or orange.  The wearer is protected by endure elements (fire) and may invoke a burning hands spell (caster level 5, DC 11) once per day.\n\nCaster Level: 5th; Prerequisites: Craft Wondrous Item, {i}burning hands{/i}, {i}endure elements{/i}; Market Price: 5,700 gp; Weight: &#151;." compset="Wondrous">
