  <thing id="ioHthMeArm" name="Hathran Mask of Mental Armor" description="This mask is painted with broad lines radiating from the eyes, each of which ends in a protective spiral. The wearer gains a +4 resistance bonus on all saving throws against mind-affecting effects.\n\nCaster Level: 9th; Prerequisites: Craft Wondrous Item, spell resistance; Market Price: 4,000 gp; Weight: &#151;." compset="Wondrous">
