  <thing id="ioHthMLang" name="Hathran Mask of Languages" description="This mask is covered with tiny letters in many languages and with pictures of strange creatures.  A mask of language is created with three languages, and the wearer can speak, understand, read, and write those languages.  The most common languages used are Chondathan, Shaaran, and Thayan Mulhorandi.\n\nCaster Level: 5th; Prerequisites: Craft Wondrous Item, {i}tongues{/i}; Market Price: 4,000 gp; Weight: &#151;." compset="Wondrous">
