  <thing id="ioHthMNigh" name="Hathran Mask of Nightseeing" description="These dark gray masks are usually decorated with owl&#146;s feathers and stylized eye markings around the eye holes.  They function exactly like {i}goggles of night{/i}, granting the wearer 60-foot darkvision.\n\nCaster Level: 3rd; Prerequisites: Craft Wondrous Item, {i}darkvision{/i}; Market Price: 8,000 gp; Weight: &#151;." compset="Wondrous">
