  <thing id="ioHthMWatB" name="Hathran Mask of Water Breathing" description="This mask is decorated with blue and green waves or fish scale patterns.  It allows the wearer to breathe water as if under the effects of a {i}water breathing{/i} spell.\nCaster Level: 5th; Prerequisites: Craft Wondrous Item, {i}water breathing{/i}; Market Price: 3,000 gp; Weight: &#151;." compset="Wondrous">
