  <thing id="ioShapMask" name="Shaporyl&apos;s Mask" description="This very rare hathran mask is decorated with tiny fancy stones and painted with elaborate patterns.  Its wearer can use {i}charm person{/i} three times per day, {i}confusion{/i} once per day, and {i}dominate{/i} person once per day.  The mask can also scintillate in a multicolored pattern for 1 round three times per day, which works like a gaze attack with a range of 30 feet.  Creatures that succumb to the gaze attack (Will negates DC 14) are dazed for 1d4+1 rounds.  The gaze attack is a mind-affecting pattern.\n\nCaster Level: 9th; Prerequisites: Craft Wondrous Item, {i}charm person{/i}, {i}confusion{/i}, {i}dominate person{/i}, {i}hypnotic pattern; Market Price: 65,000 gp; Weight: &#151;." compset="Wondrous">
