      <assignval field="CustDesc" value="An animal or plant infected by a blightspawned&#146;s blight touch becomes a blightspawned itself if its Charisma reaches 0 before its Constitution does. When a creature infected by blight touch becomes a blightspawned, it recovers all ability score points lost to the progress of the disease."/>
