  <thing id="sThfVamTch" name="Vampiric Touch" description="You must succeed on a melee touch attack. Your touch deals 1d6 points of damage per two caster levels (maximum 10d6). You gain temporary hit points equal to the damage you deal. However, you can&#146;t gain more than the subject&#146;s current hit points +10, which is enough to kill the subject. The temporary hit points disappear 1 hour later." compset="Spell" summary="Touch deals 1d6/two levels damage; caster gains damage as hp.">
