  <thing id="cTaBBblood" name="Blightblood" description="A Talontar blightlord is completely immune to all disease, magical or otherwise. Blightspawned creatures (see Chapter 6: Monsters of the East) do not attack her unless she attacks them, although they may attack other creatures in her company." compset="ClSpecial" summary="Complete immunity to all diseases, magical or otherwise.">
