  <thing id="cTaBCorBlo" name="Corrupting Blows" description="An 8th-level Talontar blightlord&#146;s black glaive gains the {i}wounding{/i} ability. A creature struck by the black glaive loses 1 hit point per round on the blightlord&#146;s action. Multiple hits by the blightlord have no additional effect and deal no additional wounding damage&#151;a creature is either wounded or it is not. The wounding damage continues until the victim is treated with a successful Heal check (DC 20) or receives magical healing." compset="ClSpecial" summary="Black glaive gains the {i}wounding{/i} ability dealing 1dmg each turn.">
