  <thing id="sDBliFear" name="Fear" description="An invisible cone of terror causes each living creature in the area {b}(a 30 ft cone shaped burst){/b} to become panicked unless it succeeds on a Will save. If cornered, a panicked creature begins cowering. (See the Dungeon Master&#146;s Guide for more information on fear-panicked creatures.) If the Will save succeeds, the creature is shaken for 1 round.\n\n{i}Material Component{/i}: Either the heart of a hen or a white feather." compset="Spell" summary="Subjects within cone flee for 1 round/level.">
