  <thing id="xRebComBli" name="Rebuke/Command Blightspawned creatures" description="Rebuke or command blightspawned creatures and evil-aligned animals or plants as an evil cleric rebukes undead. You may use this ability a number of times per day equal to 3 + your Charisma modifier. This is a supernatural ability." compset="Special" summary="Rebuke or command blightspawned creatures">
